+## Evidence Lifecycle Policy
+
+Evidence anchors from a previous session or run remain valid only when:
+1. governed scope has not changed
+2. evidence artifact still resolves
+3. no governance rule has been updated changing evaluation criteria
+
+If any condition fails: stale_evidence -> downgrade claim level.
+
+## Cross-Session Non-Equivalence Warning
+
+Session boundary is an evidence lifecycle boundary unless explicitly confirmed.
+Implicit transfer is a stale_evidence risk -> treat as unknown premise.
+
+## Forbidden Claim Conditions (updated)
